<form action="https://formsubmit.co/micros@volkman.farm" method="post">
  <p>Hey there!</p>
  <p>We really love our microgreens, and would love to share that love with you. All microgreens are packed with nutrients and health benefits, so you can't really choose wrong.</p>
  <p>Which of our microgreens would you like to learn more about?</p>
  <p>
    <select id="greens" name="green" required>
      <option disabled selected value> -- pick a green! -- </option>
      {% for green in greens %}
      <option value="{{ green.id }}">{{ green.name }}</option>
      {% endfor %}
    </select>
  </p>
  <div id="step2" style="display:none">
    <p>Excellent choice! <span id="fact"></span></p>
    <p>We'd love to share more with you! We're happy to set up an order for you, or just to chat about all the wondeful health benefits that await you. Generally customers will purchase <span id="amount"></span>oz of <span id="green"></span> a week. How much would you like?</p>
    <p>
      <select id="amount-select" name="amount-select" required>
        <option disabled selected value> -- pick an amount! -- </option>
        {% for i in (1..8) %}
        <option value="{{ i }}">{{ i }}oz</option>
        {% endfor %}
      </select>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="step3" style="display:none">
    <p>Another excellent choice! It's clear this isn't your first rodeo. Now, since we're a small family-run business with 3 homeschooled children and busy schedules, we have to be intentional about the areas and dates that we serve. Which of the following locations/dates best suits you?</p>
    <p>
      <select id="location" name="location" required>
        <option disabled selected value> -- pick a location! -- </option>
        {% for location in locations %}
        <optgroup label="{{ location.days }}">
          <option value="{{ location.id }}">{{ location.area }}</option>
        </optgroup>
        {% endfor %}
      </select>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div id="step4" style="display:none">
    <p>Now we're talking. Last question, would you mind sharing your phone number and email so we can chit-chat?</p>
    <p>
      <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" size="46" placeholder="867-5309" required>
    </p>
    <p>
      <input id="email" name="email" type="email" size="46" placeholder="crazy@about.microgreens" required>
    </p>
    <p>
      <input id="consent" type="checkbox" name="consent" required>
      <label for="consent">It's cool that we send you some email</label>
    </p>
    <p>
      <input type="submit" value="Let's chat"></input>
    </p>
  </div>
</form>

<script>
  const greens = [{%- for green in greens -%}{ id: "{{ green.id }}", name: "{{ green.name }}", fact: "{{ green.fact }}", amount: "{{ green.amount }}" },{%- endfor -%}];

  document.getElementById('greens').addEventListener('change', e => {
    const green = greens.find(g => g.id == e.target.value);
    document.getElementById('fact').innerText = green.fact;
    document.getElementById('amount').innerText = green.amount;
    document.getElementById('green').innerText = green.name;
    document.getElementById('step2').style.display = 'block';
    //document.getElementById('amount-select').value = green.amount;
  });

  document.getElementById('amount-select').addEventListener('change', e => {
    document.getElementById('step3').style.display = 'block';
  });

  document.getElementById('location').addEventListener('change', e => {
    document.getElementById('step4').style.display = 'block';
  });
</script>
